{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "27", "m": "03", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "10", "M": "36", "S": "36"}}, "news": [{"title": "Notandas Realty strengthens its legacy of craftsmanship with ultra-modern luxury innovation", "para": "Notandas Realty has carved a niche as a top-tier luxury developer within Mumbai\u2019s fast-paced real estate landscape. Boasting close to two decades of industry insight, the company specializes in stunning homes and high-end commercial areas. Guided by the visionary Mr. Harsh Jagwani, Notandas Realty leverages modern technology to ensure superior service and operational excellence.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/brand-connect-initiative/notandas-realty-strengthens-its-legacy-of-craftsmanship-with-ultra-modern-luxury-innovation/129844295?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-184560/129844295.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "brand-connect-initiative"}, {"title": "Madhuri Dixit leases commercial property in Mumbai for \u20b92.81 crore", "para": "Bollywood star Madhuri Dixit has leased a commercial space in Mumbai's One Lodha Place for a substantial monthly rent starting at \u20b94.25 lakh. The five-year agreement, registered in March 2026, includes a 67.91 sq meter unit and parking.  Rent escalates annually, culminating in a total lease value of \u20b92.81 crore over the term.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/madhuri-dixit-leases-prime-commercial-space-in-mumbai-for-281-crore/129844224?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-33784/129844224.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}, {"title": "Telangana high court refuses stay on Bhoodan land demolitions", "para": "Telangana High Court refused to halt demolitions and rehabilitation at Bhoodan lands in Khammam, citing potential harm